00:25:23,358 --> 00:25:24,723
We haven't been there for a long time.

277
00:25:25,327 --> 00:25:27,488
We can do some shopping.

278
00:25:37,472 --> 00:25:39,337
Today at Parents Day.

279
00:25:40,943 --> 00:25:42,308
I bumped into Ou-Yang.

280
00:25:48,817 --> 00:25:50,148
So, she also lives here!

281
00:25:52,187 --> 00:25:54,087
No wonder you are lost.

282
00:25:55,591 --> 00:25:56,751
You're so bad!

283
00:25:58,760 --> 00:26:01,126
As first, I thought you were after her.

284
00:26:04,466 --> 00:26:06,593
And I thought you felt for Ding.

285
00:26:08,303 --> 00:26:09,793
That is not possible!

286
00:26:13,208 --> 00:26:15,369
I love only you.

287
00:26:22,451 --> 00:26:25,978
Ou-Yang married General Liu.

288
00:26:26,955 --> 00:26:29,981
Her daughter is the classmate of Zhou.

289
00:26:35,030 --> 00:26:36,327
Perhaps,

290
00:26:37,132 --> 00:26:38,861
we can get together sometime.

291
00:26:41,069 --> 00:26:44,197
I think it's quite difficult.

292
00:26:48,710 --> 00:26:50,007
We are home now.

293
00:27:04,926 --> 00:27:06,553
It smells great!

294
00:27:19,574 --> 00:27:21,906
Hurry up, line up, kids...

295
00:27:30,986 --> 00:27:32,681
Good morning class.

296
00:27:33,055 --> 00:27:35,990
Good morning, Miss.

297
00:27:39,628 --> 00:27:40,856
Lin Xiao-Bi,

298
00:27:41,663 --> 00:27:42,994
why are you standing here?

299
00:27:43,198 --> 00:27:44,324
I am being punished.

300
00:27:44,733 --> 00:27:45,893
Why?

301
00:27:46,101 --> 00:27:47,898
Because I refuse to drink skim milk.

302
00:27:49,104 --> 00:27:50,594
Why don't you drink skim milk?

303
00:27:50,872 --> 00:27:52,999
It's horrible, only poor people drink it.

304
00:27:53,275 --> 00:27:54,606
I only take high class things.

305
00:27:59,448 --> 00:28:00,676
Kids,

306
00:28:01,717 --> 00:28:04,845
you know the story behind skim milk?

307
00:28:05,287 --> 00:28:08,017
It is a sign of the friendship
between American & us.

308
00:28:08,490 --> 00:28:10,958
You must know that other than us

309
00:28:11,159 --> 00:28:13,150
only those who go to Sunday school
can drink it.

310
00:28:13,362 --> 00:28:14,886
Ordinary people hardly get the chance.

311
00:28:15,731 --> 00:28:17,892
Since you're children of the Air Force.

312
00:28:18,233 --> 00:28:19,757
You can drink it daily,

313
00:28:20,035 --> 00:28:20,729
get it?

314
00:28:20,936 --> 00:28:22,904
Yes, Miss.

315
00:28:23,205 --> 00:28:26,072
So, drink it without hesitation.

316
00:28:27,342 --> 00:28:30,937
If not, Uncle Sam will say...

317
00:28:31,146 --> 00:28:34,172
the China kids are not behaving.

318
00:28:34,383 --> 00:28:36,180
Yes.

319
00:28:36,852 --> 00:28:38,752
Come on, be quick.

320
00:28:39,554 --> 00:28:40,578
It's almost finished.

321
00:28:40,789 --> 00:28:41,551
Finished by you?

322
00:28:41,757 --> 00:28:45,750
I mean the whole bucket of milk.

323
00:28:47,629 --> 00:28:49,096
Does it taste good?

324
00:28:50,232 --> 00:28:52,132
I... I really wonder.

325
00:28:53,602 --> 00:28:55,797
See, put in a piece of Black Sugar,

326
00:28:56,004 --> 00:28:57,665
Stir it, it tastes sweet.

327
00:28:57,873 --> 00:28:59,966
It looks like chocolate.

328
00:29:00,342 --> 00:29:03,277
Wow, chocolate! It's classy!

329
00:29:03,512 --> 00:29:05,446
Rainbow Liu is so generous.

330
00:29:06,114 --> 00:29:08,776
Shake it, then the taste comes out.

331
00:29:09,351 --> 00:29:11,683
And the color is changing!

332
00:29:11,887 --> 00:29:12,911
That's right.

333
00:29:13,388 --> 00:29:13,911
Look,

334
00:29:14,122 --> 00:29:16,317
they all want Black Sugar from Rainbow.

335
00:29:17,692 --> 00:29:18,920
Big deal!

336
00:29:24,666 --> 00:29:25,564
Sun Xiao-Zhou

337
00:29:26,802 --> 00:29:28,463
Do you want a piece of Black Sugar?

338
00:29:28,670 --> 00:29:30,103
No.

339
00:29:33,975 --> 00:29:38,139
Put the filling inside. Right,
then fold it.

340
00:29:39,181 --> 00:29:40,876
Fold it.

341
00:29:42,584 --> 00:29:46,953
Look, it's like this.

342
00:29:47,589 --> 00:29:48,647
Zhou, watch carefully.

343
00:29:48,857 --> 00:29:50,290
That's right, let mom teach you.

344
00:30:02,471 --> 00:30:03,995
Coming.

345
00:30:06,374 --> 00:30:08,365
Hi, Ding, come in please.

346
00:30:09,144 --> 00:30:10,042
No, thanks.

347
00:30:10,245 --> 00:30:12,611
Sorry to trouble you with my laundry.

348
00:30:13,415 --> 00:30:14,040
Don't mention it;

349
00:30:14,249 --> 00:30:16,080
Li should be glad to do it.

350
00:30:17,085 --> 00:30:17,813
Thank you.

351
00:30:18,086 --> 00:30:19,178
Don't you want to come in?

352
00:30:19,554 --> 00:30:20,919
No, I must leave now.

353
00:30:21,656 --> 00:30:22,714
Take care.

354
00:30:23,091 --> 00:30:24,251
See you later.

355
00:30:32,534 --> 00:30:35,059
Li, some laundry from Uncle Ding.

356
00:30:42,210 --> 00:30:47,170
How come it is like this?

357
00:30:59,594 --> 00:31:00,856
Coming...

358
00:31:03,198 --> 00:31:04,995
- Ding. - Ping, I am sorry.

359
00:31:08,203 --> 00:31:08,794
Uncle Ding.

360
00:31:14,342 --> 00:31:15,502
Li, have you seen a paper note?

361
00:31:21,783 --> 00:31:22,909
You mean this one?

362
00:31:28,657 --> 00:31:29,783
Have you read it?

363
00:31:34,996 --> 00:31:36,224
Did your mother read it?

364
00:31:47,876 --> 00:31:49,138
Ding, what's the matter?

365
00:31:50,245 --> 00:31:51,337
I am sorry, Ping.

366
00:32:02,490 --> 00:32:03,821
Dad, charge up!

367
00:32:18,273 --> 00:32:21,436
Go... Hurry up!

368
00:32:53,742 --> 00:32:55,039
Why don't you go in?

369
00:32:56,678 --> 00:32:57,702
It's not so convenient.

370
00:32:58,313 --> 00:33:00,110
This isn't your first time! Don't be shy?

371
00:33:04,486 --> 00:33:05,714
Thank you.

372
00:33:05,920 --> 00:33:07,251
It doesn't matter, it's ok.

373
00:33:11,359 --> 00:33:13,953
I will go home now.

374
00:33:18,566 --> 00:33:19,794
Take care, Mrs Hu.

375
00:33:26,341 --> 00:33:27,569
What's up?

376
00:33:28,877 --> 00:33:30,071
Mr Hu was arrested.

377
00:33:30,545 --> 00:33:33,241
They suspect he is a spy.
He is now under investigation.

378
00:33:38,753 --> 00:33:40,015
Don't worry.

379
00:33:40,722 --> 00:33:43,020
As long as he is innocent,

380
00:33:43,725 --> 00:33:45,192
he will be fine.

381
00:33:46,961 --> 00:33:48,553
But you never know what will happen!

382
00:33:51,833 --> 00:33:54,597
Ding, you are from the Bureau
of Political Security.

383
00:33:55,136 --> 00:33:56,603
Can you give Mr Hu a hand?

384
00:34:00,675 --> 00:34:01,801
Ping,

385
00:34:02,677 --> 00:34:05,237
don't get involved in this matter.

386
00:34:08,416 --> 00:34:09,815
Let's go in first.

387
00:34:10,752 --> 00:34:11,912
Let's talk inside.

388
00:34:57,932 --> 00:34:59,593
How's dad's accordion?

389
00:35:01,770 --> 00:35:03,499
Do you want to learn?

390
00:35:04,672 --> 00:35:05,195
No!

391
00:35:05,406 --> 00:35:05,929
Do you want to know...

392
00:35:06,141 --> 00:35:08,268
how he wooed me?

393
00:35:09,577 --> 00:35:13,707
Your father took me to his plane.

394
00:35:13,915 --> 00:35:16,679
It was a beautiful morning.

395
00:35:17,051 --> 00:35:18,211
We went to the airport.

396
00:35:18,486 --> 00:35:20,477
I said "How can it be?

397
00:35:20,688 --> 00:35:21,712
You're breaking the rules."

398
00:35:22,323 --> 00:35:23,813
He said "Never mind,"

399
00:35:24,125 --> 00:35:27,993
Each pilot can break the rules 3 times.

400
00:35:28,363 --> 00:35:32,094
So, the first time was with me.

401
00:35:33,034 --> 00:35:33,363
On that day,

402
00:35:33,568 --> 00:35:37,334
he flew very slow,

403
00:35:37,539 --> 00:35:40,133
we saw all the houses,

404
00:35:40,341 --> 00:35:43,833
the people and the animals.

405
00:35:44,813 --> 00:35:46,804
They are all under our feet.

406
00:35:47,348 --> 00:35:48,975
I could even...

407
00:35:49,184 --> 00:35:50,845
see your grandparents.

408
00:35:51,152 --> 00:35:53,985
How can I not help falling in love?

409
00:35:54,589 --> 00:35:56,250
How about the second time?

410
00:35:56,457 --> 00:35:58,789
Oh, it was for your sister Li.

411
00:35:58,993 --> 00:36:00,620
How come I don't remember?

412
00:36:01,229 --> 00:36:03,060
I want the third time?

413
00:36:03,598 --> 00:36:04,121
If there is a third,

414
00:36:04,332 --> 00:36:06,163
your father will never be allowed to fly!

415
00:36:07,302 --> 00:36:08,701
Never be allowed to fly again...

416
00:36:12,941 --> 00:36:15,876
Line up, one by one.

417
00:36:16,244 --> 00:36:16,869
Kid, you should line up.

418
00:36:17,078 --> 00:36:18,511
Time for skim milk!

419
00:36:23,918 --> 00:36:26,443
How come you have such a big piece
of Black Sugar!

420
00:36:27,922 --> 00:36:28,946
Father gave that to me.

421
00:37:01,956 --> 00:37:05,483
Zhou, do you have Black Sugar too?

422
00:37:06,261 --> 00:37:08,286
Keep yours,

423
00:37:09,731 --> 00:37:11,494
try mine first.

424
00:37:13,701 --> 00:37:15,066
Take a seat.

425
00:37:17,038 --> 00:37:17,629
Thank you.

426
00:37:18,039 --> 00:37:18,835
Welcome.

427
00:37:37,425 --> 00:37:38,585
Hurry up!

428
00:37:48,670 --> 00:37:50,297
Is Sun Han-Sun here?

429
00:37:51,339 --> 00:37:52,169
Yes.

430
00:37:52,640 --> 00:37:55,632
We'll take you to the Commander's office.
You are now under arrest for spying.

431
00:37:56,210 --> 00:37:57,507
Have you got it wrong?

432
00:37:57,779 --> 00:37:59,542
This is the warrant.

433
00:38:05,887 --> 00:38:08,185
Ping, I am fine.

434
00:38:10,825 --> 00:38:12,452
I have been loyal to the country,

435
00:38:12,660 --> 00:38:13,718
I did nothing wrong.

436
00:38:18,466 --> 00:38:19,558
I will be fine.

437
00:38:22,837 --> 00:38:23,997
I will follow you.

438
00:38:24,238 --> 00:38:25,569
Take him away.

439
00:38:28,076 --> 00:38:30,476
Han-Sun!

440
00:38:37,118 --> 00:38:39,848
Are you Jin Wen-Ping?

441
00:38:41,356 --> 00:38:42,345
Yes.

442
00:38:42,757 --> 00:38:44,520
You're accused of being pro-Communist.

443
00:38:44,993 --> 00:38:47,018
We'll take you into custody.

444
00:38:47,628 --> 00:38:48,424
Take her away.

445
00:38:53,101 --> 00:38:54,500
Search the house.

446
00:38:54,702 --> 00:38:55,760
Yes.

447
00:38:56,871 --> 00:39:00,136
The sun will rise tomorrow.

448
00:39:00,341 --> 00:39:03,799
The flowers will bloom next year, too.

449
00:39:04,112 --> 00:39:07,343
But the beautiful bird flies
and never returns.

450
00:39:07,548 --> 00:39:10,016
Zhou, Li, come on, follow me.

451
00:39:11,586 --> 00:39:14,851
My little bird of youth will never return.

452
00:39:15,523 --> 00:39:16,319
Zhou, Li,

453
00:39:16,958 --> 00:39:17,947
something happened to your family.

454
00:39:57,065 --> 00:39:58,464
Give way...

455
00:40:09,911 --> 00:40:11,208
Search again!

456
00:40:12,780 --> 00:40:14,111
Search every inch of it.

457
00:40:15,850 --> 00:40:17,681
Ding.

458
00:40:18,252 --> 00:40:19,219
Yes.

459
00:40:20,588 --> 00:40:22,988
Little girl, look

460
00:40:23,424 --> 00:40:26,985
We didn't take away anything.

461
00:40:27,495 --> 00:40:28,553
Remember that.

462
00:40:29,964 --> 00:40:30,794
Ding,

463
00:40:31,766 --> 00:40:35,258
Iet them sign on the warrant.

464
00:40:35,470 --> 00:40:36,960
Then, tell the girls that...

465
00:40:38,005 --> 00:40:40,633
their parents will be gone for a while.

466
00:40:44,612 --> 00:40:48,946
And this place...
it will be sealed tomorrow.

467
00:40:51,419 --> 00:40:53,785
Ask the neighbors to take care of them.

468
00:40:53,988 --> 00:40:55,046
Yes, sir.

469
00:40:56,057 --> 00:40:57,718
All right, let's go.

470
00:41:43,738 --> 00:41:43,999
I'll take you...

471
00:41:44,205 --> 00:41:46,571
to Uncle Kou's home.

472
00:41:48,409 --> 00:41:49,899
They'll take care both of you.

473
00:41:57,451 --> 00:41:59,476
I want daddy's accordion.

474
00:42:00,555 --> 00:42:02,113
Don't take anything useless.

475
00:42:08,362 --> 00:42:10,159
You will stop going to school
for the time being.

476
00:42:12,300 --> 00:42:14,234
Help Auntie Kou to do some chores.

477
00:42:17,705 --> 00:42:19,195
Come with me now.

478
00:42:21,509 --> 00:42:22,806
You'll be back.

479
00:42:28,716 --> 00:42:29,410
Li,

480
00:42:29,884 --> 00:42:31,749
are the lunch boxes ready yet?

481
00:42:31,953 --> 00:42:33,113
Yes, they are ready.

482
00:42:33,788 --> 00:42:36,120
- Wake Ah-Lun up. - He is dressing.

483
00:42:37,525 --> 00:42:39,755
Take care of the baby while I am out.

484
00:42:39,961 --> 00:42:40,928
Yes.

485
00:42:41,162 --> 00:42:44,131
Come on, be a good girl.

486
00:42:44,532 --> 00:42:45,829
Take care.

487
00:42:50,271 --> 00:42:52,501
Ah-Lun, get up for breakfast.

488
00:42:53,975 --> 00:42:55,306
Girls,

489
00:42:55,643 --> 00:42:57,770
- did you sleep well? - All right.

490
00:42:58,279 --> 00:43:00,247
Everyday is the same, dressing up...

491
00:43:00,448 --> 00:43:02,643
and eating breakfast.

492
00:43:03,551 --> 00:43:06,019
You're lazy!

493
00:43:06,220 --> 00:43:07,414
Why don't you eat breakfast?

494
00:43:07,989 --> 00:43:08,683
It will help you grow tall...

495
00:43:08,889 --> 00:43:11,255
- and strong. - I am tall enough.

496
00:43:11,459 --> 00:43:12,448
You are not!

497
00:43:12,893 --> 00:43:13,860
Come on, eating more...

498
00:43:14,061 --> 00:43:16,086
will help you become smart.

499
00:43:16,297 --> 00:43:17,594
Come on, eat your breakfast now.

500
00:43:17,898 --> 00:43:21,197
Mom, I want Lion's Head meat balls
tonight.

501
00:43:21,469 --> 00:43:24,768
- Lion's Head again?
- You naughty boy!

502
00:43:24,972 --> 00:43:26,439
Li is not your maid.

503
00:43:26,641 --> 00:43:28,575
Lion's Head is delicious
but you can't have it everyday.

504
00:43:28,776 --> 00:43:31,643
This is a difficult time.
We should be thrifty.

505
00:43:31,846 --> 00:43:32,710
Just let him eat what he likes,

506
00:43:32,913 --> 00:43:35,211
what a nag!

507
00:43:35,416 --> 00:43:40,410
Come on, let's have breakfast.

508
00:43:41,322 --> 00:43:43,119
You look beautiful!

509
00:43:44,125 --> 00:43:45,490
Because of their help.

510
00:43:45,693 --> 00:43:47,217
So I will have a break,

511
00:43:47,428 --> 00:43:48,622
I am going to play mahjong.

512
00:43:49,830 --> 00:43:51,058
Who is coming this early?

513
00:43:51,265 --> 00:43:52,493
Who is it?

514
00:43:59,273 --> 00:44:01,332
Are the Sun sisters...

515
00:44:01,976 --> 00:44:03,273
Iiving here?

516
00:44:03,644 --> 00:44:04,872
Yes, they are.

517
00:44:05,212 --> 00:44:06,645
I am the driver of General Liu.

518
00:44:06,981 --> 00:44:09,609
Ms Liu would like to bring them a gift.

519
00:45:37,338 --> 00:45:39,431
Stay where you are. Wait right here.

520
00:45:45,045 --> 00:45:46,342
Sign this.

521
00:45:58,859 --> 00:46:00,053
The meeting begins.

522
00:46:15,376 --> 00:46:16,365
Dad, I miss you,

523
00:46:16,577 --> 00:46:18,238
are you going to abandon us?

524
00:46:19,814 --> 00:46:23,181
Don't be silly! I will never abandon you.

525
00:46:27,555 --> 00:46:28,351
Are you taking good care of your sister?

526
00:46:28,556 --> 00:46:29,079
Yes!

527
00:46:29,356 --> 00:46:32,348
Good! How is your grade in Math?

528
00:46:32,560 --> 00:46:34,050
I haven't got it yet.

529
00:46:34,628 --> 00:46:35,560
Haven't got it...

530
00:46:43,737 --> 00:46:44,999
Wait here for me,

531
00:46:45,639 --> 00:46:47,231
I have to talk to Uncle Ding.

532
00:47:35,723 --> 00:47:38,453
I was accused of flying to
the Communist Zone during the war.

533
00:47:51,939 --> 00:47:54,305
You knew my purpose is going there.

534
00:47:59,880 --> 00:48:01,905
I just wanted to bring back Li with me.

535
00:48:15,229 --> 00:48:16,958
They are accusing me of treason.

536
00:48:21,936 --> 00:48:23,699
But the people I saw,

537
00:48:25,739 --> 00:48:27,297
the things I did,

538
00:48:29,476 --> 00:48:31,000
you were with me all that time.

539
00:48:34,782 --> 00:48:38,809
You knew what I said, what I did.

540
00:48:47,861 --> 00:48:49,123
You witness it all.

541
00:49:08,282 --> 00:49:09,613
Help me!

542
00:49:29,837 --> 00:49:33,170
"General Liu"

543
00:49:34,308 --> 00:49:35,366
Why was he arrested?

544
00:49:35,943 --> 00:49:37,069
Treason, Sir.

545
00:49:37,811 --> 00:49:39,335
He is unyielding.

546
00:49:45,285 --> 00:49:46,616
Who are these girls?

547
00:49:47,821 --> 00:49:49,015
His daughters.

548
00:49:51,325 --> 00:49:52,883
Pity!

549
00:50:07,541 --> 00:50:08,508
Mom.

550
00:50:08,942 --> 00:50:10,102
Zhou.

551
00:50:12,012 --> 00:50:13,070
Mom...

552
00:50:18,552 --> 00:50:19,849
Ding.

553
00:50:21,021 --> 00:50:22,318
Why did you take her along?

554
00:50:23,524 --> 00:50:25,321
Hasn't she dragged us down enough?

555
00:50:26,727 --> 00:50:27,751
Mom...

556
00:50:28,028 --> 00:50:29,427
I am not your mom.

557
00:50:31,298 --> 00:50:32,560
Because of you,

558
00:50:33,233 --> 00:50:35,497
your dad snuck into the Communist zone

559
00:50:37,004 --> 00:50:38,096
