01:16:06,065 --> 01:16:07,726
Sun is dead for sure.

835
01:16:10,169 --> 01:16:13,297
But why was the woman arrested too?

836
01:16:14,206 --> 01:16:15,696
It was to make the show perfect.

837
01:16:17,276 --> 01:16:18,971
You know what kind of person Ding is.

838
01:16:20,779 --> 01:16:26,411
