845
01:17:08,060 --> 01:17:09,493
Didn't she go to the Women's Association?

846
01:17:09,995 --> 01:17:11,053
No, General.

847
01:17:12,965 --> 01:17:14,694
Not very much a General's wife.

848
01:17:15,434 --> 01:17:19,131
