855
01:17:45,864 --> 01:17:48,025
I think it is time to do some gardening.

856
01:17:49,501 --> 01:17:50,991
Yes, General.

857
01:18:01,613 --> 01:18:03,478
Sis, are you doing well here?

858
01:18:03,716 --> 01:18:04,683
I am fine.

859
01:18:06,618 --> 01:18:07,915
Let me tell you a secret.

860
01:18:08,654 --> 01:18:12,317
Uncle Ding turned in dad.

861
01:18:14,026 --> 01:18:17,860
Dad was executed because of Uncle Ding.

862
01:18:18,697 --> 01:18:20,426
It's because Uncle Ding fell for mom.

863
01:18:25,504 --> 01:18:27,028
Never tell the others.

864
01:18:37,316 --> 01:18:39,614
Why are you so quiet?

865
01:18:41,053 --> 01:18:42,782
You're a spy,

866
01:18:42,988 --> 01:18:44,546
you filed a report that sent my dad
to his death.

867
01:18:50,662 --> 01:18:52,186
How do you know your father is dead?

868
01:18:52,598 --> 01:18:54,964
I saw the execution at the Dry River.

869
01:18:57,569 --> 01:18:58,593
Who took you there?

870
01:18:58,804 --> 01:19:00,499
Auntie Liu and her driver.

871
01:19:12,317 --> 01:19:15,184
Now I will file a report on Auntie Liu
and her driver.

872
01:19:31,069 --> 01:19:32,263
How was your test today?

873
01:19:32,571 --> 01:19:33,435
Not bad.

874
01:19:33,906 --> 01:19:34,873
Miss, excuse me, I have to go now.

875
01:19:36,742 --> 01:19:37,538
Mom, I am back.

876
01:19:37,743 --> 01:19:39,040
Good evening, Auntie Liu.

877
01:19:39,745 --> 01:19:40,211
Good girl.

878
01:19:40,412 --> 01:19:41,436
Is that for me?

879
01:19:41,780 --> 01:19:42,439
Yes,

880
01:19:43,048 --> 01:19:45,642
I made some sandwiches for you.

881
01:19:45,918 --> 01:19:46,612
After the snack,

882
01:19:46,819 --> 01:19:48,218
you can go for a movie.

883
01:19:48,420 --> 01:19:49,114
Bravo!

884
01:19:51,890 --> 01:19:53,687
So, let's hurry up
and finish our homework.

885
01:19:53,892 --> 01:19:54,324
Sure!

886
01:19:54,760 --> 01:19:55,852
Try this dress first.

887
01:19:56,061 --> 01:19:56,755
Ok!

888
01:19:59,264 --> 01:20:01,323
Auntie Liu, you are beautiful!

889
01:20:04,970 --> 01:20:08,030
Zhou, I have a present for you too.

890
01:20:08,807 --> 01:20:10,001
See if you like it or not.

891
01:20:11,009 --> 01:20:12,408
Open it now.

892
01:20:15,247 --> 01:20:16,339
"Prince of Tears"

893
01:20:19,451 --> 01:20:21,351
This is our little secret,

894
01:20:22,054 --> 01:20:23,578
