898
01:20:39,938 --> 01:20:43,032
No, but Daddy did.

899
01:20:46,945 --> 01:20:48,469
Rainbow, how do you like it?

900
01:20:48,847 --> 01:20:51,543
Mom, it looks nice! I love pink.

901
01:20:51,750 --> 01:20:52,808
I know.

902
01:20:53,452 --> 01:20:55,352
