908
01:22:43,228 --> 01:22:44,286
Hello!

909
01:22:44,630 --> 01:22:46,598
Yes...

910
01:22:55,774 --> 01:22:56,866
Yang...

911
01:23:07,953 --> 01:23:09,511
Phoenix, come here.

912
01:23:10,255 --> 01:23:14,521
Auntie, I didn't do anything wrong.

913
01:23:15,427 --> 01:23:17,395
Come here,

914
01:23:17,596 --> 01:23:19,564
