915
01:23:19,898 --> 01:23:22,924
No, I do not.

916
01:23:23,769 --> 01:23:24,861
General.

917
01:23:41,920 --> 01:23:43,251
I am sorry...

918
01:23:43,455 --> 01:23:45,423
I've broken your vase.

919
01:24:19,791 --> 01:24:23,454
That night she knew her time had come.

920
01:24:25,163 --> 01:24:28,894
