921
01:24:30,035 --> 01:24:33,971
It has 266 pearls,

922
01:24:34,539 --> 01:24:35,972
a family treasure.

923
01:25:25,624 --> 01:25:27,751
Come back...

924
01:25:54,519 --> 01:25:55,645
Hurry up!

925
01:26:52,177 --> 01:26:54,077
