926
01:26:54,279 --> 01:26:55,644
Nonsense!

927
01:27:18,403 --> 01:27:21,463
Zhou, let me take you home.

928
01:27:21,773 --> 01:27:23,832
No, thanks, I can go home alone.

929
01:27:25,410 --> 01:27:27,401
Rainbow, see you tomorrow at the statue.

930
01:27:27,746 --> 01:27:29,680
All right, see you.

931
01:27:29,881 --> 01:27:32,611
- Miss, let's go. - See you!

932
01:27:38,723 --> 01:27:42,124
That night,
Madam Liu finally made her exit.

933
01:27:43,161 --> 01:27:45,527
She left behind her beauty and beliefs

934
01:27:46,331 --> 01:27:48,458
