935
01:28:17,395 --> 01:28:19,727
Zhou, why are you still standing here?

936
01:28:19,931 --> 01:28:21,057
Go to class.

937
01:28:52,931 --> 01:28:55,229
Why isn't Rainbow here today?

938
01:28:55,433 --> 01:28:58,231
Mom won't allow me to talk.

939
01:29:03,942 --> 01:29:08,436
Rainbow then disappeared in Zhou's life.

940
01:29:11,583 --> 01:29:15,781
People said Madame Ou-Yang Liu
was a Communist spy.

941
01:29:16,421 --> 01:29:19,720
General Liu
was sent to the military court too.

942
01:29:20,258 --> 01:29:23,955
Rainbow was sent to
the "Woman's Association for custody."

943
01:29:24,562 --> 01:29:27,759
They want to check
if she was influenced by her mother.

944
01:29:28,833 --> 01:29:31,893
People said,
the Communists are powerful...

945
01:29:32,103 --> 01:29:35,971
at brain-washing kids.

946
01:29:37,509 --> 01:29:40,967
Zhou thought it was all her fault.

947
01:29:41,946 --> 01:29:44,380
She felt that she was a sinner.

948
01:29:45,116 --> 01:29:47,016
Not unworthy of Rainbow's friendship,

949
01:30:18,450 --> 01:30:19,815
Mom!

950
01:30:24,055 --> 01:30:25,215
Zhou.

951
01:30:34,499 --> 01:30:36,262
Let me take a good look at you!

952
01:30:39,537 --> 01:30:42,062
Oh, you look thin.

953
01:30:43,808 --> 01:30:45,605
Did you drink skim milk at school?

954
01:30:48,179 --> 01:30:51,512
Has Uncle Ding taken good care of you?
Have you missed Mom?

955
01:31:03,228 --> 01:31:05,628
You grew bigger & taller.

956
01:31:16,141 --> 01:31:17,506
- Ping! - Uncle Ding!

957
01:31:20,445 --> 01:31:21,878
We will have extra dish tonight.

958
01:34:00,672 --> 01:34:01,661
Mom, I am back.

959
01:34:01,873 --> 01:34:02,999
You're home!

960
01:34:04,242 --> 01:34:05,607
Did you pay attention well in class?

961
01:34:05,810 --> 01:34:06,777
Yes.

962
01:34:07,879 --> 01:34:08,743
Li come here,

963
01:34:08,946 --> 01:34:11,278
Iet me take a good look at you.

964
01:34:13,017 --> 01:34:14,985
