967
01:34:18,856 --> 01:34:21,051
Deliver them to Auntie Zhang's.

968
01:34:21,259 --> 01:34:23,887
Remember to let her sign the bill,
they are on credit.

969
01:34:24,128 --> 01:34:25,060
All right.

970
01:34:36,874 --> 01:34:38,102
Yes, coming.

971
01:34:42,647 --> 01:34:44,205
Hi, Ding.

972
01:34:44,515 --> 01:34:45,573
Ping.

973
01:34:45,783 --> 01:34:46,875
Look, you are too generous

974
01:34:49,654 --> 01:34:50,916
Are you busy making money?

975
01:34:52,423 --> 01:34:54,186
