976
01:34:54,592 --> 01:34:56,787
About seven to eight hundred a day.

977
01:34:58,463 --> 01:35:01,227
Give me the laundry,
I'll ask Li to do for you.

978
01:35:01,666 --> 01:35:05,625
Li, come over. The laundry first,

979
01:35:05,837 --> 01:35:07,134
the dumplings later.

980
01:35:09,607 --> 01:35:10,835
Please go inside.

981
01:35:11,142 --> 01:35:13,440
Where is Zhou?

982
01:35:14,612 --> 01:35:15,909
I just saw her.

983
01:36:18,776 --> 01:36:21,836
Li is a big girl now.

984
01:36:23,214 --> 01:36:25,182
I'd like to send her study in the city.

985
01:36:25,983 --> 01:36:27,143
What do you think?

986
01:36:36,294 --> 01:36:39,092
This is a good idea.

987
01:37:18,169 --> 01:37:19,636
Would you go inside?

988
01:37:30,515 --> 01:37:31,709
Mom, I am back.

989
01:37:36,153 --> 01:37:37,347
You're home

990
01:37:48,666 --> 01:37:49,997
We are discussing...

991
01:37:50,201 --> 01:37:51,964
Li's schooling.

992
01:37:54,539 --> 01:37:55,870
Have you greeted Uncle Ding yet?

993
01:37:56,073 --> 01:37:57,062
Uncle Ding.

994
01:37:59,810 --> 01:38:01,903
Uncle Ding has a friend in the city.

995
01:38:02,280 --> 01:38:03,941
Li can...

996
01:38:04,148 --> 01:38:05,615
stay with them.

997
01:38:09,086 --> 01:38:10,348
Li come here.

998
01:38:16,394 --> 01:38:17,383
Take this.

999
01:38:18,296 --> 01:38:20,321
Go and have some noodles.

1000
01:38:21,532 --> 01:38:23,591
You can go to a movie later.

1001
01:38:24,235 --> 01:38:25,532
Don't be too late.

1002
01:38:26,070 --> 01:38:27,628
We'll get changed.

1003
01:38:36,547 --> 01:38:39,516
I just want to let you know,
Ding and I are getting married.

1004
01:38:53,898 --> 01:38:58,426
Li, is Uncle Ding's shirt ready?

1005
01:39:06,644 --> 01:39:08,043
Why are you still wearing pajamas?

1006
01:39:08,546 --> 01:39:11,174
Go get changed,
we're going to take photos.

1007
01:39:18,389 --> 01:39:19,515
Move now.

1008
01:39:21,392 --> 01:39:25,385
Mom, it's always Uncle Ding's laundry.
Have you got anything else to say?

1009
01:39:27,365 --> 01:39:29,560
They are right,
you're finally going to marry Ding.

1010
01:39:34,505 --> 01:39:36,735
I just want you to iron the shirt.

1011
01:39:38,142 --> 01:39:39,939
Why did you say such a thing to me?

1012
01:39:41,245 --> 01:39:42,371
Mom, everbody...

1013
01:39:42,580 --> 01:39:44,343
is talking behind us?

1014
01:39:44,582 --> 01:39:45,606
They are laughing at us!

1015
01:39:46,350 --> 01:39:48,875
Because of you,
Uncle Ding sent dad to jail.

1016
01:39:49,220 --> 01:39:50,585
And Dad was shot dead.

1017
01:39:52,323 --> 01:39:53,620
He killed Dad,

1018
01:39:54,025 --> 01:39:55,993
now he wants to sleep in Dad's bed.

1019
01:39:57,595 --> 01:40:00,587
I just can't stand it.

1020
01:40:03,634 --> 01:40:06,467
What happened to you?

1021
01:40:26,991 --> 01:40:28,686
Li, come here.

1022
01:40:38,502 --> 01:40:40,936
You know why I do this.

1023
01:40:46,777 --> 01:40:49,746
I just want you girls to live better.

1024
01:40:54,452 --> 01:40:56,010
You think I know nothing...

1025
01:40:56,220 --> 01:40:57,983
of the gossip?

1026
01:41:00,491 --> 01:41:02,482
So what if this is true?

1027
01:41:06,430 --> 01:41:08,125
It's history.

1028
01:41:10,367 --> 01:41:12,392
We have to survive anyway.

1029
01:41:18,476 --> 01:41:24,005
That time you came to see me in custody.
I scolded you,

1030
01:41:28,085 --> 01:41:29,643
your father returned
to the Communist zone,

1031
01:41:30,688 --> 01:41:33,213
all because of you.

1032
01:41:35,159 --> 01:41:37,992
That's why he was charged with spying.

1033
01:41:44,101 --> 01:41:46,035
I never said a harsh word to you before,

1034
01:41:47,905 --> 01:41:50,203
because you were not born by me.

1035
01:41:54,745 --> 01:41:59,648
That was the first time I scolded you
and I regretted.

1036
01:42:14,398 --> 01:42:17,333
Mom is just an ordinary woman.

1037
01:42:18,502 --> 01:42:22,336
I just want you girls to live better.

1038
01:42:25,042 --> 01:42:33,245
Mom, I am sorry...

1039
01:42:33,751 --> 01:42:35,946
Do you understand, Li?

1040
01:42:53,704 --> 01:42:55,069
Are you ready?

1041
01:42:55,840 --> 01:42:57,205
Yes, we are ready.

1042
01:42:58,642 --> 01:42:59,734
Let's go.

1043
01:43:22,766 --> 01:43:27,066
"Story of lost lovers"

1044
01:44:03,407 --> 01:44:06,308
Li, take good care of your sister.

1045
01:44:06,510 --> 01:44:07,408
Yes.

1046
01:44:07,611 --> 01:44:08,475
Ding.

1047
01:44:09,914 --> 01:44:10,778
Are you ready?

1048
01:44:11,148 --> 01:44:12,137
Coming.

1049
01:44:15,486 --> 01:44:17,351
Send them to school now, don't be late.

1050
01:44:18,589 --> 01:44:19,851
Let's go to school now.

1051
01:44:22,426 --> 01:44:23,393
Take care.

1052
01:44:23,594 --> 01:44:24,959
- Goodbye, Mom. - See you, Mom.

1053
01:44:27,831 --> 01:44:30,857
Don't make supper, let's eat out.

1054
01:44:33,203 --> 01:44:34,397
Come back early.

1055
01:46:48,605 --> 01:46:52,097
You're back! I missed you.

1056
01:47:53,670 --> 01:47:56,468
Where have you been?

1057
01:47:58,509 --> 01:48:00,409
How have you been?

1058
01:48:17,461 --> 01:48:19,895
Since our seperation,

1059
01:48:20,097 --> 01:48:21,792
I was imprisoned on Green lsland.

1060
01:48:23,267 --> 01:48:24,996
I always thought I would see you again.

1061
01:48:26,904 --> 01:48:28,428
But then one day,

1062
01:48:31,341 --> 01:48:34,208
my heart broke.

1063
01:48:35,445 --> 01:48:37,470
And that was the day you were executed.

1064
01:48:49,526 --> 01:48:51,551
I almost gave up my desire to live.

1065
01:48:59,236 --> 01:49:01,534
Until I received Ding's first letter,

1066
01:49:08,178 --> 01:49:09,509
I could...

1067
01:49:10,047 --> 01:49:12,743
never forgive myself
for Han-Sun's death.

1068
01:49:14,384 --> 01:49:16,784
He urged me to prove his innocence.

1069
01:49:17,788 --> 01:49:19,813
Such a simple request,

1070
01:49:20,857 --> 01:49:22,654
but I refused to do so.

1071
01:49:25,229 --> 01:49:27,424
When I found out the verdict.

1072
01:49:28,665 --> 01:49:30,656
It was too late to reverse the judgment.

1073
01:49:32,236 --> 01:49:33,863
On that day, I accompanied him
to the execution ground.

1074
01:49:34,838 --> 01:49:36,863
