1075
01:49:38,942 --> 01:49:40,842
I didn't see hatred in his eyes.

1076
01:49:42,846 --> 01:49:44,837
Bearing an unforgivable guilt.

1077
01:49:46,416 --> 01:49:48,247
I tidied everything for him.

1078
01:49:50,687 --> 01:49:52,552
I know Li has always disliked me.

1079
01:49:54,091 --> 01:49:56,025
But how can I tell her that...

1080
01:49:56,760 --> 01:50:00,287
