01:52:21,405 --> 01:52:22,963
she likes her very much.

1106
01:52:30,113 --> 01:52:33,913
Do you remember...

1107
01:52:37,120 --> 01:52:41,113
how we met?

1108
01:52:47,164 --> 01:52:48,529
That time,

1109
01:52:51,034 --> 01:52:53,730
you picked up my book "Prince of Tears."

1110
01:52:56,840 --> 01:53:00,241
You asked me
why is it named "Prince of Tears."

1111
01:53:02,879 --> 01:53:04,141
I said,

1112
01:53:05,849 --> 01:53:09,785
because the Prince saw
and hated the injustices of the society,

1113
01:53:11,021 --> 01:53:12,648
so tears filled his eyes.

1114
01:53:14,624 --> 01:53:19,027
You said, just so simple?

1115
01:53:23,767 --> 01:53:24,995
I said...

1116
01:53:28,705 --> 01:53:33,369
tears are the beginning of the story.

1117
01:53:36,813 --> 01:53:38,041
Afterwards...

1118
01:53:41,151 --> 01:53:42,618
everything will be changed.

1119
01:54:02,172 --> 01:54:03,571
On that day,

1120
01:54:05,542 --> 01:54:07,976
we leaned on to each other.

1121
01:54:10,313 --> 01:54:14,841
She turned the pages one by one

1122
01:54:16,920 --> 01:54:20,879
and explained the meaning...

1123
01:54:21,992 --> 01:54:28,261
of each picture to me
the hidden meaning behind the words...

1124
01:54:30,901 --> 01:54:38,137
and the pictures.

1125
01:54:44,748 --> 01:54:46,238
Do you recall her name?

1126
01:54:55,425 --> 01:54:57,086
Ou-Yang Qian-Jun.

1127
01:55:07,237 --> 01:55:10,468
I betrayed her, and betrayed you.

1128
01:55:14,144 --> 01:55:16,237
When people look at me,

1129
01:55:17,414 --> 01:55:20,872
Their eyes are telling me...

1130
01:55:26,389 --> 01:55:28,380
you betrayed the man who loved you,

1131
01:55:29,159 --> 01:55:30,490
and the friend who trusted you,

1132
01:55:31,728 --> 01:55:35,687
Then, married a man
who brought down your family.

1133
01:56:11,267 --> 01:56:14,794
Once again Ping hears
that familiar accordion.

1134
01:56:15,705 --> 01:56:18,799
There is a nameless sorrow in her heart.

1135
01:56:19,976 --> 01:56:23,343
She knows Han-Sun will never return
after this visit.

1136
01:56:23,813 --> 01:56:25,872
And she misses him so.

1137
01:56:29,352 --> 01:56:34,153
In a trance,
she returns to the day they were arrested.

1138
01:56:35,158 --> 01:56:36,716
She sits in the kitchen.

1139
01:56:37,460 --> 01:56:39,690
Listens to the music.

1140
01:56:40,730 --> 01:56:43,756
Rolls some cigarettes for Han-Sun.

1141
01:56:54,444 --> 01:56:56,036
I love your music.

1142
01:57:01,351 --> 01:57:02,716
I love your simplicity.

1143
01:57:05,622 --> 01:57:06,987
I love your honesty.

1144
01:57:09,859 --> 01:57:11,258
I love you...

1145
01:57:13,363 --> 01:57:14,853
till the end of the world.

1146
01:57:23,840 --> 01:57:25,899
Why do you make so many cigarettes?

1147
01:57:32,315 --> 01:57:33,782
You'll leave on a mission soon.

1148
01:57:36,019 --> 01:57:37,816
So better bring more with you.

1149
01:57:45,228 --> 01:57:46,490
Why is it so noisy out there?

1150
01:57:54,204 --> 01:57:57,640
Let's take a look.

1151
01:58:17,093 --> 01:58:19,288
And she will never forget

1152
01:58:20,230 --> 01:58:26,260
his last glance before parting.

1153
01:58:32,142 --> 01:58:33,268
The story...

1154
01:58:33,476 --> 01:58:37,537
floats away.

1155
01:58:38,448 --> 01:58:41,849
One still clings to it.

1156
01:58:42,752 --> 01:58:45,778
And one can only rely on hope now.

1157
01:59:02,472 --> 01:59:04,133
Han-Sun returned today.

1158
01:59:07,977 --> 01:59:11,469
From 1 950 to 1 954 during
the martial law era in Taiwan

1159
01:59:11,681 --> 01:59:17,210
Over 3000 people were sentenced to death,
and more than 8000 were jailed.

1160
01:59:17,420 --> 01:59:21,618
Their aggregate prison terms
exceeded 1 0,000 years.

1161
01:59:24,694 --> 01:59:29,757
This movie is based on a true story.

1162
01:59:33,102 --> 01:59:36,367
The father was executed in 1 954 accused
of treason & re-established in 2005.

1163
01:59:36,573 --> 01:59:39,098
His remains are yet to be found.

1164
01:59:42,078 --> 01:59:44,444
The mother remarried in 1 956
and had two more children.

1165
01:59:44,647 --> 01:59:48,174
She is 86 and still lives in Taiwan.

1166
01:59:50,987 --> 01:59:53,683
Ding married Ping and spent
his life quietly in Taichung

1167
01:59:53,890 --> 01:59:57,656
and died in 1992 at the age of 79.

1168
02:00:00,563 --> 02:00:05,830
Li has had a happy family life in Taipei
with two children.

1169
02:00:08,271 --> 02:00:13,004
Zhou became an actress
and was a top star in the 1960s.

1170
02:00:15,311 --> 02:00:19,805
It's all by-gones.
